
This folder contains bits and pieces needed to fully configure boardspace.net
from a generic unix server.   These are things that might be overlooked at
first, if moving to a new server.

SSH setup.

 Remove root login access - require login to a non-root account first

 Set up passwordless authentication for tantrix/boardspace backup.  Some
obscure ssh setup was needed, resulting in the files in the ssh.tar file
here.  These set up a public/private key pair for public key authenticaion
and enable that flavor or authentication to ssh



